{"tid":1762886,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"內地男睹港人抗爭：了不起","createTime":"2019-11-30T02:20:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T05:39:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"55a50743878c00dcb947ab97db9284d55a0892fd","tid":1762886,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T02:20:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191130/HXW4Q64ETIKP5D3IXL43ZOAJIA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191130%2FHXW4Q64ETIKP5D3IXL43ZOAJIA%2F&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY9eKooxOH8zUMv7fiy4eq7s%3D&h=68c520e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191130%2FHXW4Q64ETIKP5D3IXL43ZOAJIA%2F&h=14669b5e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191130/HXW4Q64ETIKP5D3IXL43ZOAJIA/</a><br />\n<br />\n內地男睹港人抗爭：了不起<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】「因為我們在內地聽到一些報道，還有一些廣播電視，我只能說我們聽的是一面之詞，我覺得還是到實地來看一下，把這歷史時刻記住。」想不到首次來港的內地人李先生，昨日中午其中一個參觀的「景點」是理工大學，是如他所說，只是路過也好，特意也好，他終究能親眼觀看事實，不禁讚嘆港人為了爭取民主自由而抗爭，勇氣令人敬佩。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191130/large/1575042193_216b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191130%2Flarge%2F1575042193_216b.jpg&h=e32a564e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吳小姐看到校園留有血，想及學生被圍困多日慘況，不禁落淚。黃麗英攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上班族見血迹落淚<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：警撤離 理大之戰拘1,377人<br />\n<br />\n眼前理大一片狼藉，李先生慨嘆：「香港的學子很不簡單，我覺得內地的學子沒有這種勇氣。香港人民也了不起，為了自由，為了民主，能這樣堅持正義，給我們內地的人做了一個很好的榜樣。」<br />\n<br />\n雖然李先生不清楚五大訴求的詳情，但他認為要活得有意義，「就是要活得明白，堅持自己認為是對的，為了真理，為了自由去抗爭」，他坦言在內地爭取自由絕不容易。<br />\n<br />\n上班途經理大的市民吳小姐，目睹理大的破損不禁鼻子一酸，掉下淚來，「超級震撼，喺天橋見到遮陣嗰陣已經好心悒，去到正門入嚟就更加崩潰。」她解釋並非在意建築物毀爛，而是眼前景物彷彿將留守者抗爭的畫面呈現，「當日戰場上，學生有幾驚」。<br />\n<br />\n她沿路看見抗爭者留下的血迹、眼罩和口罩，讚賞抗爭者的決心及勇氣，同時也替他們感到很難過。對於警方指今次以和平方式撤出理大，她不表認同，「早就應該要（撤離），唔應該圍守十幾日」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者馮智敏、江子堯"},{"pid":"03b11e52a06da809409e119485ff71c5d5f458ef","tid":1762886,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T02:37:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c712aed01c215238644818c0d7fe60c95ff986b","tid":1762886,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03b11e52a06da809409e119485ff71c5d5f458ef","tid":1762886,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T02:37:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T02:51:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"befd9289370e552a2990dbf9176d27ca80c49383","tid":1762886,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T02:57:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dad67d6613958631e88b4f706b410538135898b","tid":1762886,"uid":12628,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T03:05:43.000Z","msg":"香港抗爭者我地係付出左沉重嘅代價，同時，港共同警甴，你地一樣都要！"},{"pid":"bddc6d3608172751e8e4d25a5125e5ff0c293c89","tid":1762886,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T05:39:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n輸出革命"}]}